---
title: Speedy Caramelized Beyond Meat® Bowls with Sticky Lemongrass-Scented Rice
description: This quick and easy bowl is inspired by the bold flavours of Vietnam! Sweet and savoury sing together when Beyond Meat® is caramelized with brown sugar and zesty aromatics. Get to know fragrant lemongrass at the dinner table tonight!

